05:16:40 - Outro Cutscene - Grablins Ending

Diggers version 1.94 is a rare, late North American release, originally developed in the UK by Millennium Interactive Ltd and published in the USA by Millennium Media Group.  This release addresses many of the complaints made against previous versions of the game.

This release introduces:
* keyboard controls
* new level graphics
* revised level design to allow more conflict between teams
* improved UI design for shop, bank and main menus
* CD audio
